
# Meloob

An 80s themed playlist sharing website.




## Deployment

Run on Docker

```bash
  docker build -t u21528790 .
  docker run --name app -p 3001:3001 u21528790
```
```bash
  docker stop app
  docker rm app
```

## API Reference

#### Get all users

```http
  GET /api/users
```
Gets a list of all users.



#### Signup

```http
  POST /api/signup
```

| Parameter | Type     | Description                       |
| :-------- | :------- | :-------------------------------- |
| `username`      | `string` | **Required**. Username of the new user. |
| `email`      | `string` | **Required**. Email address of the new user. |
| `password`      | `string` | **Required**. Hashed password of the new user (Argon2i)|
| `profile_picture`      | `string` | **Required**. Url for the new user. |
| `followers`      | `array` | **Required**. Empty list of followers |
| `following`      | `array` | **Required**. Empty list of followers |
| `playlists_created`      | `array` | **Required**. Empty list of playlists |
| `playlists_saved`      | `array` | **Required**. Empty list of playlists |
| `description`      | `string` | **Required**. Empty description. |


Creates a new user after signup.

##### Example Response

```javascript
{
    "id": "64e3f1bc9f12a61d2c5a4c58",
    "username": "newuser",
    "email": "newuser@example.com",
    "password": "hashedPassword",
    "profile_picture": "profilePic.jpg",
    "followers": [],
    "following": [],
    "playlists_created": [],
    "playlists_saved": [],
    "description": "New user bio."
}
```


